text:
Good job, Mei.
Here, have some refreshments.

Thanks~
These cold ones really hit the spot.

You seem like you've been putting in a lot of effort.
Practicing without much rest, right?

Got a bit carried away and
lost track of when to stop, huh~?

It's great that you're enjoying yourself,
but make sure to take breaks, okay?

But it's really nice when everyone comes
together and works hard, isn't it?

Yeah...
I wish it could continue like this forever.
